summary: Hello and welcome , This is a mod retexture for the woodcutters axe .
descriptionHtml:
Hello and Welcome ! 

Let me introduce myself , Abandoner is the name .
Me and my Modder in crime  started to notice a lot of vannila items are not lore friendly anymore .
And if they are . they are not much to download in loose files .
Me and my new team will work on lots of new vannila retextures 
becuase we noticed what was going on . 
I will make sure the mods/textures will be carefully tested ( also with ENB presets ) . Wich i focus upon for greater effect .
My mods look just as great without enb . Its just a personal taste .

For any [font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]reqeusts[/size][/font] on [font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]vannila[/size][/font] goods , Always welcome ! 
We will work on the mod till its perfect .

For future notice we will focus upon some more new projects 

including :

Weapons 
Armour/Shields 
Housing  * lorefriendly/Adventurer 
More Textures 



This is Our first mod/texture , And with that a new modding team was born .

Greetings Team DLD : [b][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]Dusty Lore Dynasty ( Abandoner & Majuko )


Great thanks to Mujuko for testing this mod .

<----\_____ This mod can [/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=5]not[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4] be used in other mods without [/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=5]permission[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4] ,, First [/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=5]ask[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4] .. ___/---->
